### Enrichment
Telegram Bot API supports MarkdownV2 parse mode for formatting. telegramify-markdown (PyPI, updated Apr 2026) converts raw Markdown to Telegram-compatible format. The universal capture pattern (URL/photo/voice/text/forward) aligns with AI4PKM vision of automated capture. Consider mentioning telegramify-markdown for rendering markdown back to Telegram in notifications.

